---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Bienvenido a Sacs"
  description="Tu cuenta ha sido creada exitosamente."
>

<section class="welcome-page">
  <div class="welcome-inner">
    <div class="welcome-check">
      <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none">
        <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="24" fill="var(--color-secondary)"/>
        <path d="M15 24l6 6 12-12" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <h1 class="welcome-title">Tu cuenta está lista</h1>
    <p class="welcome-desc">Tienes 7 días gratis para explorar todas las funciones de Sacs. No se realizará ningún cobro durante tu prueba.</p>

    <div class="welcome-next">
      <h2 class="welcome-next-title">Siguientes pasos</h2>
      <div class="welcome-steps">
        <div class="welcome-step">
          <span class="welcome-step-num">1</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Revisa tu correo</strong>
            <span>Te enviamos los datos de acceso a tu cuenta.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="welcome-step">
          <span class="welcome-step-num">2</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Configura tu catálogo</strong>
            <span>Agrega tus primeros productos o importa desde Excel.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="welcome-step">
          <span class="welcome-step-num">3</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Empieza a vender</strong>
            <span>Tu punto de venta está listo. Haz tu primera venta hoy.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a class="welcome-btn" href="https://app.sacscloud.com" target="_blank">Ir a mi cuenta</a>
    <a class="welcome-link" href="/">Volver al inicio</a>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.welcome-page {
  min-height: 80vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: calc(71px + 48px) 20px 48px;
}

.welcome-inner {
  max-width: 480px;
  text-align: center;
}

.welcome-check {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
}

.welcome-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--color-text-primary);
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  margin: 0 0 var(--space-3);
}

.welcome-desc {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0 0 var(--space-10);
}

.welcome-next {
  text-align: left;
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
  padding: var(--space-6);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
}

.welcome-next-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-text-primary);
  margin: 0 0 var(--space-5);
}

.welcome-steps {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-4);
}

.welcome-step {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: var(--space-3);
}

.welcome-step-num {
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: #fff;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.welcome-step strong {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-text-primary);
}

.welcome-step span {
  font-size: 0.8125rem;
  color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
}

.welcome-btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 16px;
  background: var(--color-text-primary);
  color: #fff;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  border-radius: var(--radius-full);
  text-decoration: none;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.welcome-btn:hover {
  background: #333;
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.welcome-link {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
  text-decoration: none;
}

.welcome-link:hover { color: var(--color-primary); }
</style>
